4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals looking to become cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. The program lasts 16 weeks and includes 3 live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced topics like cloud security and cyber threat intelligence. Upon completion, students receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. The program supports both English and Spanish languages, requiring no previous experience. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop